507
00:57:23.443 --> 00:57:24.812
My blood.

508
00:57:32.219 --> 00:57:34.889
All this blood wasn't mine?

509
00:58:05.853 --> 00:58:07.588
Let's go!

510
00:58:08.522 --> 00:58:10.224
